@startuml
' Use template styling (assuming monochrome, etc.)
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

title US2.2.2: Register and Update Vessel Records - System Sequence Diagram (SSD)

autonumber
actor "Port Authority Officer" as Authority
participant ":System" as System

activate Authority
'--- Register Scenario ---
Authority -> System : attempts to register a new vessel with details (IMO number, vessel name, vessel type, owner, vessel status)
activate System
System --> Authority : validates IMO number format (7 digits + check digit)
System --> Authority : confirms successful registration of the vessel record
deactivate System

'--- Update Scenario ---
... Authority selects an existing vessel record to update ...
Authority -> System : requests to update vessel record details (IMO number, newName, newType, newOwner, newStatus)
activate System
System --> Authority : validates IMO number format
System --> Authority : confirms successful update of the vessel record
deactivate System

'--- Search Scenario ---
... Authority wants to search vessel records ...
Authority -> System : searches vessels by (IMO number, name, or operator)
activate System
System --> Authority : returns matching vessel records
deactivate System

deactivate Authority

@enduml
